title: Monitor This - 20 songs by various artists
description:

Widespread Panic - Boom Boom Boom (Free Somehow, Widespread Records)

Jeremy Fisher - High School (Field Manual, Barsuk)

Liam Finn - Second Chance (I&#039;ll Be Lightning, Yep Roc)
Matt Costa - Mr. Pitiful (Unfamiliar Faces, Universal Republic)
Nada Surf - See These Bones (Lucky, Barsuk)
Radiohead - Bodysnatchers (In Rainbows, TBD/ATD)
Bullet For My Valentine - Scream, Aim, fire (Scream, Aim, Fire, 20/20 Jive Records)
The Mars Volta - Wax Simulacra (The Bedlam in Goliath, Universal Mowtown)
The Spill Canvas - All Over You (No Really, I&#039;m fine, Sire)
Bell X1 - Rocky Took a Lover (Flock, Yep Roc)
Gary Louris - True Blue (Vagabonds, Ryko)
Magnetic Fields - California Girls (Distortion, Nonesuch)
Kate Nash - Foundations (Made of Bricks, Fiction/Geffen)
Ben&#039;s Brother - Stuttering (Beta Male Fairy Tales, Virgin/Restless)
Idiot Idiot - Retina and the Sky (Wolves, Reprise)
Natasha Bedingfield - Pocketful of Sunshine (Pocketful of Sunshine, Epic)

This CD was intended for promotional use only. It is not for sale. If you like these songs, please buy the indicated albums.
